# Claude Code Agent Model Defaults
# ==================================
# These environment variables control the behavior of the multi-agent orchestration system
# Edit these values as needed, then run: source scripts/load-env.sh
#
# Available Variables:
#
# | Variable | Options | Default | Description |
# |----------|---------|---------|-------------|
# | `CLAUDE_CODE_SUBAGENT_MODEL` | haiku, sonnet, opus | sonnet | Model for SubAgent specialists |
# | `CLAUDE_CODE_EFFORT_LEVEL` | low, medium, high | medium | Thoroughness level |
# | `CLAUDE_CODE_ORCHESTRATOR_MODEL` | haiku, sonnet, opus | opus | Orchestrator model (optional) |
# | `CLAUDE_CODE_WORKER_MODEL` | haiku, sonnet, opus | sonnet | Worker model (optional) |
# | `CLAUDE_CODE_SCOUT_MODEL` | haiku, sonnet, opus | haiku | Scout model (optional) |
#
# ==================================

# SubAgent Model Configuration
# Options: haiku, sonnet, opus
CLAUDE_CODE_SUBAGENT_MODEL=sonnet

# Agent Effort Level
# Options: low, medium, high
CLAUDE_CODE_EFFORT_LEVEL=high

# Orchestrator Model Override
CLAUDE_CODE_ORCHESTRATOR_MODEL=opus

# Default Worker Model
# Options: haiku, sonnet, opus
CLAUDE_CODE_WORKER_MODEL=sonnet

# Scout Model for Lightweight Tasks
# Options: haiku, sonnet, opus
CLAUDE_CODE_SCOUT_MODEL=haiku